# Alembic Migrations — Brand Sniper

Async database migrations (asyncpg) for the Brand Sniper monorepo.

## Usage
```bash
cd deployments
uv run alembic upgrade head        # Apply all pending migrations
uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"  # Generate a new migration
```

## Notes
- All SQLModel schemas are defined in `packages/shared_utils/src/shared_utils/models.py`.
- Alembic's `env.py` imports models from `shared_utils` and uses `SQLModel.metadata` as `target_metadata`.
- Migrations use an async engine (`asyncpg`).